    "title": "[Kernel] Simplify `get_kv_cache_layout` and cache `use_trtllm_attention` env-dependent bit",
    "user": {
      "login": "NickLucche",
      "id": 10706289,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEwNzA2Mjg5",
